import { Button, TextField } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

export default function login() {
  return (
    <form noValidate autoComplete="off">
        <TextField 
        label="Email"
        name="email"
        variant="outlined"/>
        <TextField 
        label="Email"
        name="email"
        variant="outlined"/>
        <Button 
        type = "submit"
        variant="contained"
        size="large">Start</Button>
        </form>
  )
}
